one big performance...

283
00:14:30,090 --> 00:14:31,390
..as protection

284
00:14:31,850 --> 00:14:33,419
against the dreaded

285
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:35,770
black hole of your heart.

286
00:14:42,370 --> 00:14:43,750
Well, guess what,
