300
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:22,490
Don't you put your hands on me!

301
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,940
Have you been drinking?

302
00:16:41,010 --> 00:16:43,469
You, escort Mr Healy
out of here! You...

303
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:45,920
- where's that fucking ambulance?!
- It's all right.

304
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:55,660
It's all right, it's all right.

305
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:05,890
Drive.

306
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:08,010
Drive!

307
00:18:00,030 --> 00:18:02,870
- I'm shaking.
- How much did you see?

308
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:06,610
My monitor went dead.
The attack on Gibson.

309
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:08,449
It didn't stop there.

310
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:10,749
- What a way for the whole thing to end.
- End?

311
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:12,329
What do you mean?

312
00:18:12,330 --> 00:18:14,559
We can't possibly represent him now.

313
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:15,869
Why not?

314
00:18:15,870 --> 00:18:18,289
I've never seen violence
like that before in my life.

315
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:19,760
What have we just witnessed?

316
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,789
The very thing you described.

317
00:18:21,790 --> 00:18:23,349
Their deep obsession
with each other.

318
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:25,609
The emergence under duress
of "Bad Paul".

319
00:18:25,610 --> 00:18:27,409
If Larson doesn't find evidence

320
